class_description:
Checked exception thrown when a lookup of UserPrincipal fails because
 the principal does not exist.

params.param_description: the principal name; may be null

Methods.method_description: Constructs an instance of this class.

return_description: the user principal name or null

Methods.method_description:
Returns the user principal name if this exception was created with the
 user principal name that was not found, otherwise null.
